OL,12,FThe dream of home ownership could be
OL,13,Fsnatched away from thousands of
OL,14,Fcouncil tenants under a big shake-up
OL,15,Fby the government.
OL,17,FLabour is worried people are buying
OL,18,Fproperties faster than new ones are
OL,19,Fbeing built, but new rules could
OL,20,Fdampen demand in a scheme introduced
OL,21,Fby Margaret Thatcher in the 1980s.
