OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,FRight to Buy has allowed social
OL,7,Fhousing tenants to own their homes at
OL,8,Fa significant discount with around two
OL,9,Fmillion properties sold.
OL,11,FWhile the policy has boosted rates of
OL,12,Fhome ownership it has also been blamed
OL,13,Ffor increasing the number of families
OL,14,Fliving in temporary accommodation.
