OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News London, the
OL,7,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,8,Fsaid: "People should be able to buy
OL,9,Ftheir home if they've lived in it and
OL,10,Fraised their family in it for many
OL,11,Fyears, but we think people get a
OL,12,Fdiscount (on buying it) far too soon.
OL,14,F"At the moment, the discount that is
OL,15,Fgiven to people under the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment meant the taxpayer wasn't
OL,17,Fgetting value for money and we
OL,18,Fcouldn't replace the stock.
