OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,F"And of course in London we have a
OL,7,Fparticular problem with people in
OL,8,Ftemporary accommodation, one in four
OL,9,Fchildren in the classroom in London
OL,10,Fare in temporary accommodation."
OL,12,FA shakeup of the rules could mean
OL,13,Ftenants have to live in their homes
OL,14,Ffor up to a decade before buying them
OL,15,Fat a discount - an increase from the
OL,16,Fcurrent minimum of three.
OL,18,FDiscounts have already been cut and,
OL,19,Fin future, sales of all new council
OL,20,Fhomes could be blocked to replenish
OL,21,Fhousing stocks.
