OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,FEmily Hills has been a council tenant
OL,7,Ffor more than 30 years and lives in a
OL,8,Fthree-bed terrace in Sunbury-on-Thames
OL,9,Fwith six of her eight children and is
OL,10,Fkeen to buy.
OL,12,F"It's always been my dream to buy a
OL,13,Fhouse and one of my twins will buy it
OL,14,Fwith me," Emily said.
OL,16,F"Eventually we'd like to extend to
OL,17,Fmake it bigger because we've got quite
OL,18,Fa large family and maybe one day move.
