OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,FHousing campaigner Kwajo Tweneboa said
OL,7,FRight to Buy fueled the housing
OL,8,Fcrisis, adding: "It is the most
OL,9,Fdamaging policy introduced in respect
OL,10,Fto not just social housing, but
OL,11,Fhousing in general, and has massively
OL,12,Ffueled the crisis that we're facing
OL,13,Ftoday.
OL,15,F"Since the introduction of the Right
OL,16,Fto Buy scheme we've sold off more than
OL,17,F2 million council properties.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/14
