OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,FThe maximum discount in London was
OL,7,F136,400. But following a government
OL,8,Freview maximum discounts were reduced
OL,9,Fin November 2024 to #16,000 or #38,000
OL,10,Fin the boroughs of Barking and
OL,11,FDagenham and Havering.
OL,13,FHousing and homelessness charity
OL,14,FShelter said the government was right
OL,15,Fto cut the discount.
OL,17,F"At the moment we have more than
OL,18,F186,000 people who are now homeless in
OL,19,FLondon," said Charlie Trew, Head of
OL,20,FPolicy at Shelter.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/14
