OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,F"We are losing so many social homes,
OL,7,Fparticularly in London, due to Right
OL,8,Fto Buy and the government are looking
OL,9,Fat Right to Buy to try and reduce
OL,10,Fthose discounts and make sure that
OL,11,Fthey can replace the social homes.
OL,13,F"We've lost more than 2 million homes
OL,14,Fthanks to Right to Buy in the whole of
OL,15,Fthe UK and only 2 per cent of those
OL,16,Fhave been built back in London.
OL,18,F"That's 315,000 social rented homes
OL,19,Fthat have been lost thanks to Right to
OL,20,FBuy.
