OL,3,CWill Labour rip up the rules on Right
OL,4,Cto Buy to protect council homes?
OL,6,F"With record levels of homelessness
OL,7,Fthis is a real, real problem because
OL,8,Fcouncils have nowhere to put people
OL,9,Fwhen they come to them for help.
OL,11,F"Homelessness is at record levels both
OL,12,Fin London and across the whole
OL,13,Fcountry. It is really serious.
OL,15,F"We've had a 12 per cent increase in
OL,16,Fhomelessness in London even just in
OL,17,Fthe last year.
OL,19,F"It is a breaking point right now, and
OL,20,Fwe desperately need to fix it."
